xyz.fsgik.common.base

类 FsRandom.Builder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.fsgik.common.base.FsRandom.Builder<T>
  • 封闭接口:
    FsRandom<T>

    public static class FsRandom.Builder<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder to create FsRandom.

    Use score(int, Object) and score(int, Supplier) methods to specify the score for specified value. When call the FsRandom.next() method, each value's probability of occurrence is proportional to the percentage of its specified score to the total score.

      • score

        public <R extends T> FsRandom.Builder<R> score(int score,
                                               T value)
        Specifies the score for specified value.

        When call the FsRandom.next() method, each value's probability of occurrence is proportional to the percentage of its specified score to the total score, the specified value will be returned in that probability.

        类型参数:
        R - type of random
        参数:
        score - the score
        value - specified value
        返回:
        this builder

      • score

        public <R extends T> FsRandom.Builder<R> score(int score,
                                               java.util.function.Supplier<T> supplier)
        Specifies the score for specified supplier.

        When call the FsRandom.next() method, each value's probability of occurrence is proportional to the percentage of its specified score to the total score, the value gotten from specified supplier will be returned in that probability.

        类型参数:
        R - type of random
        参数:
        score - the score
        supplier - specified supplier
        返回:
        this builder
